I'm now integrating the image-based PDF display into the main page, ensuring the `pdfPages` array is correctly used for image source URLs. I have implemented a fallback to handle scenarios where the PDF data is unavailable. This includes an alert icon to ensure the user does not get a blank page. The pages are now stacked, and the fallback ensures a seamless user experience.


